# Smart Expense Tracker — Overhaul Walkthrough

## What Was Done

### Server ([server.js](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/server/server.js))
- Added `GET /summary` — per-category totals, monthly breakdown, this-month total, count
- Added `GET /PUT /budget` — set and read a monthly spending budget  
- Better input validation (positive amounts, non-empty category, whitespace trimming)
- Email normalization on signup/login
- Expenses now returned sorted newest-first

### Client (React/Vite)

**Design System ([index.css](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/index.css))**  
Complete dark design system with CSS custom properties: `--bg-base: #080c18`, violet accent `#6c63ff`, glassmorphism utilities, animated keyframes, Inter font from Google Fonts.

**New Components**
- [Navbar.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/components/Navbar.jsx) — Sticky glassmorphism nav with active route highlighting, user email, logout
- [EditModal.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/components/EditModal.jsx) — Modal dialog with category pill grid, replaces `window.prompt`

**Updated Components**
- [StatsCard.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/components/StatsCard.jsx) — Animated easing counter, colored icon badge
- [ExpenseChart.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/components/ExpenseChart.jsx) — Gradient horizontal bars per category, emoji icons, sorted by spending

**Pages**
- [Login.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/pages/Login.jsx) — Animated multi-color gradient BG, glassmorphism card, password visibility toggle, loading spinner, inline error
- [Dashboard.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx) — Greeting with time-of-day, 4 animated stat cards, budget progress bar, full chart, recent transactions panel
- [AddExpense.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/pages/AddExpense.jsx) — ₹-prefix big amount input, category pill grid (7 categories with emoji)
- [History.jsx](file:///home/great/Documents/Web%20Development%20Projects/full%20stack/smart-expense-tracker-starter/client/src/pages/History.jsx) — Search/filter bar, styled table with emoji category chips, inline delete confirm (no browser dialogs), EditModal integration, total footer

